OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781432282
OL,3,CMan, 88, dies after suffering serious
OL,4,Cinjuries in car crash
OL,6,FKent Police is appealing for
OL,7,Fwitnesses, CCTV and dashcam footage
OL,8,Fare following a fatal collision in
OL,9,FHerne Bay.
OL,11,FThe Emergency Services were called to
OL,12,FHeart in Hand Road, Herne Bay, at
OL,13,F11.36am on Friday 22 May 2026,
OL,14,Ffollowing reports of a collision
OL,15,Finvolving two vehicles.
OL,17,FAn 88 year old man was taken to a
OL,18,Flocal hospital after sustaining
OL,19,Fserious injuries and has since died.
OL,21,FHis family have been made aware.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
