OL,3,CMan, 88, dies after suffering serious
OL,4,Cinjuries in car crash
OL,6,FOfficers from the Serious Collision
OL,7,FInvestigation Unit are making
OL,8,Fenquiries into the circumstances
OL,9,Fsurrounding the incident.
OL,11,FThey are urging anyone who saw the
OL,12,Fcollision, or who might have seen the
OL,13,Fvehicles beforehand, to contact Kent
OL,14,FPolice.
OL,16,FMotorists who were in the area are
OL,17,Furged to check for any dashcam
OL,18,Ffootage, which may assist the
OL,19,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
